title: Modifications to the speech board code.
message:
Modifications to the speech board code.

This commit features three changes:
1) Modified how words are edited after speech. Introduced the ability to allow users to select words and repeat the speech process.
2) User is taken to the newly created board
3) Users can now only access the speech board feature in edit mode.

title: Added support for creating new boards by speaking a set of words.
message:
Added support for creating new boards by speaking a set of words.

The implementation searched for each word and if it finds just one it downloads it. If there are multiple words it presents a grid with all the results.

title: Added a toast message for the delete and save buttons in the create button activity.
message: Added a toast message for the delete and save buttons in the create button activity.

title: Implemented an Alert dialog when the user pressed the back button on the create button activity.
message:
Implemented an Alert dialog when the user pressed the back button on the create button activity.

The user is asked if he wants to quit without saving his changes.

title: Fixed about page.
message:
Fixed about page.

The social buttons were too large.

title: Implemented support for generating PDF documents from pictograms.
message: Implemented support for generating PDF documents from pictograms.

title: Fixed the bug that made the action bar not display properly when unlocking the display.
message:
Fixed the bug that made the action bar not display properly when unlocking the display.

There were two bugs, one in portrait mode where the action bar wasn't positioned immediately below the status bar but lower. The other in landscape mode where the action bar was positioned lower and more to the left, leaving a gap on the right side.
